Package: tscsdep
Type: Package
Title: Tools for analyzing country-year time-series-cross-sectional data with spatial and temporal dependence
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jude Hays [aut, cre]
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Jude",
                  family = "Hays",
